# Precomputed visualization data (issue #7): built in CI, published as the
# `data` release asset, and delivered into files/iwac-visualizations/ by the
# admin "Pull latest data" job — never committed. Static map geometry lives in
# asset/geo/ (committed). The one exception is sentiment-arbiter.json, which is
# externally sourced (sibling IWAC-sentiment-analysis study, not HF) and
# committed by the curator so CI can ship it in the archive.
/asset/data/*
!/asset/data/sentiment-arbiter.json
